{"word":"G2998 - λατομέω - latoméō - lat-om-eh'-o - Hew","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">λατομέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">latoméō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">lat-om-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hew</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வெட்டு"},{"paragraph":"to cut stones, to hew out stones"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as the first part of <a href=\"#/G2991 - λαξευτός - laxeutós - lax-yoo-tos'/2991\">G2991</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G5114 - τομώτερος - tomṓteros - tom-o'-ter-os/5114\">G5114</a>; to <i>quarry:</i> - hew.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}